snippet.title: The Sims 3 Generations Producer's Walk Through
snippet.description: Learn more about the upcoming release of The Sims 3 Generations as our producers walk you through the many new ways you can live every age to the fullest!  Push your Sims further than you ever thought possible. Play with more fun. Play with more drama. Play with more mischief at every age.
